Class CellInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.Parent

              • tables.CellInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class CellInfo
extends javafx.scene.layout.VBox
    CellInfo is a VBOw that holds the information needed to display individual information about a cell link in the table as well as controlling the ability to link through all of the other cell Links in each CellInfo.
    Author:
    lisaketcham
